{"id": 2859, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有哪些“跟着影视剧过人生”的习惯？", "description": "知道不是真的，但我还是忍不住。（题图来自：视觉中国©️Stockbyte）", "record_count": 1918, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190325224225XuP3KwlCkD5dq2ch.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-03T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 338689, "content": "看了很多电影电视剧 \n想象着自己过着那样的人生 起起伏伏悲悲喜喜\n回归着之后的自己\n以后的我们会怎么样\n我希望彼此过得很好\n有好友 家人 爱人 共欢彼此的生活\n我希望老了以后有人牵着我 步履蹒跚的我们\n彼此相爱\n我想念的你  你过的怎么样 \n我爱的家人 \n", "image": "img/option/option/20190411173932SjsAQ8qXenu2PZL3.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634897}, {"id": 337667, "content": "不开心的时候看喜剧，看搞笑综艺", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629350}, {"id": 337669, "content": "破产姐妹，闲了看，不开心了看，自暴自弃时看，吃饭时看，贯穿我的这一年，每次看完心情就好很多，原来自己还不是很糟糕呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629376}, {"id": 343814, "content": "看《请回答1988》特别想吃泡面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508716}, {"id": 337938, "content": "看《北上广不相信眼泪》，总想找男主那样男朋友。真实又不真实的人设啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276954}, {"id": 338208, "content": "老友记", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002334}, {"id": 339239, "content": "觉得老公出轨时看了金粉世家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637975}, {"id": 340520, "content": "跟着女主角买衣服、饰品、手机壳、鞋子&包包……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559568}, {"id": 335405, "content": "一个人吃外卖的时候看《老友记》，好像身边也有了很多人陪伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 420, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 338478, "content": "《恋与》中我为了遇见许墨，所以我想像女主一般优秀，然而我就制定了大学目标", "image": "img/option/option/20190410214144KG51gIrhZ0V8E7Ok", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634015}, {"id": 335408, "content": "跟人讲道理，总能想到一些影视剧台词金句，比如《武林外传》里的佟掌柜说过.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 337457, "content": "葛优瘫啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628202}, {"id": 335410, "content": "每到没钱了穷得吃土都找来《破产姐妹》看一看找点慰藉", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335411, "content": "很丧的时候跟着《马男》一起丧", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 338744, "content": "丧的时候看无耻之徒就觉得自己的生活咬咬牙还过得去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619568}, {"id": 337732, "content": "每次上台讲话之前脑子里说一句我是麦瑟尔夫人hhhhhh", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628172}, {"id": 338254, "content": "国产难得有好剧，余罪算不错的了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630674}, {"id": 339791, "content": "坐火车没有什么想看的剧的时候，就看《最完美的离婚》。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640153}, {"id": 337235, "content": "我不把影视剧当人生，我经常认为也许自己的人生就是一部影视剧或者一篇小说，可能我现在打的字也只是短短几句话描述过去的片段而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435514}, {"id": 337237, "content": "感同身受 \n", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1624663}, {"id": 337238, "content": "想要恋爱时，就会看《恶作剧之吻》跟着傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525473}, {"id": 337239, "content": "睡前看邪恶力量，基本一会就睡着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329728}, {"id": 337240, "content": "老友记 看了10年 人生的酸甜苦辣啊 都是体会", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582723}, {"id": 337243, "content": "因为近视带了眼镜，之后看了镇魂，嗯，学会了新的扶眼镜的姿势，现在我扶眼镜基本上都是这样了。", "image": "img/option/option/20190403112227QETFRktrYmba5fod", "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486579}, {"id": 337244, "content": "不怎么看电视剧，看电影比较多，但是除非和我很像，产生共情，我一般都不会带入，觉得自己活的已经挺精彩的了", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 337245, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627189}, {"id": 337246, "content": "听《我爱我家》做家务，度过朴素的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 337247, "content": "有一年圣诞节 爸妈都出门应酬 我一个人在家大扫除 收音机里传来难忘今宵——我真的忘不了那天", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 337759, "content": "跟着 《This Is Us》过周末，看到动情，环顾四周，手机里那么热闹，一个人还挺孤独。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629454}, {"id": 338272, "content": "我的《请回答1988》《家有儿女123》《破产姐妹》百看不腻！！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615676}, {"id": 337249, "content": "永远相信爱的力量——童话镇里的true love真的太吸引我了", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1585122}, {"id": 338017, "content": "破产姐妹………和姐妹一起插科打诨………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169574}, {"id": 337250, "content": "因为夏目友人帐，决定顺从本心做一个温柔的人。", "image": "img/option/option/20190403114347GCULe1wai5Dzbv4A.jpg", "praise_count": 218, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627191}, {"id": 337251, "content": "看都挺好的时候\n老想和对象\n开小会", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627205}, {"id": 337763, "content": "摩登家庭追了有快十年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599540}, {"id": 337252, "content": "学火影跑步姿势和忍术结印", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320043}, {"id": 337253, "content": "看《都挺好》的时候\n老想和对象\n开小会", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627205}, {"id": 337254, "content": "有时候心情不好想飚脏话，就看绝命毒师，跟里面的杰西学脏话。。。bitch。。。mtherfk。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1521238}, {"id": 338022, "content": "学习影视套路，反套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614147}, {"id": 337255, "content": "成功养成吃完饭看美剧的习惯", "image": "img/option/option/20190403120036rI4etEfFRaqDw7vW", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538312}, {"id": 337256, "content": "成功养成吃完饭看美剧的习惯", "image": "img/option/option/201904031200149YMWuf3Ca6QSi8AG", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538312}, {"id": 337512, "content": "最近在看老爸老妈浪漫史~感觉自己身边也有这样的朋友在~嗯~很下饭~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614198}, {"id": 337257, "content": "生活中的日常感动都来自屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78499}, {"id": 337258, "content": "像《One day》那样，喜欢着某个人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537109}, {"id": 337259, "content": "《武林外传》经典下饭剧啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 192, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 337515, "content": "想家的时候看《家有儿女》 不开心的时候看《家有儿女》", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588215}, {"id": 337260, "content": "每周六看一集《this is us》治愈", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130199}, {"id": 337264, "content": "最近看《伦敦生活》，觉得自己和fleabag一样是个内心空虚又没什么朋友的女孩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627246}, {"id": 337265, "content": "每次看神话背景的电视剧，都觉得自己是下凡历劫的仙女", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625523}, {"id": 337778, "content": "觉得自己没用成为女强人很沮丧的时候，看都挺好里面的苏明玉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629899}]}